    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, you've found it! This car is an absolute gem and has been totally babied\u2014seriously, it's in pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next big adventure. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to find a home with someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
