    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality 2021 Lexus RX 350 F-Sport in Ultra White over a striking Circuit Red leather interior. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows absolutely zero signs of wear. The exterior paint is in pristine condition, enhanced by a professional ceramic coating, with no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. The 20-inch F-Sport wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the leather seats are firm with no bolster compression, and the dash is free of any UV damage or scratches. Every electronic feature, including the Mark Levinson surround sound system and the 12.3-inch navigation display, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively at Lexus dealerships. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a virtually new luxury SUV. Includes both original keys, all weather-mats, original window sticker, and a clean title.",
      "price": 43900.0,
